Apa ini makhluk hidup?

22
00:03:17,708 --> 00:03:19,167
Cepat tangkap ini!

23
00:03:29,583 --> 00:03:30,958
Apa kau tak apa-apa?

24
00:03:31,417 --> 00:03:33,875
